        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "={\n  \"model\": \"llama3:latest\",\n  \"prompt\": \"Write a professional and friendly morning walking recommendation email.\\n\\nAddress the user by name: {{ $json.userName }}.\\n\\nFollow this structure exactly:\\n\\n1. Greet the user by name.\\n2. One short introductory sentence.\\n3. Show the walk details, each on a separate line, in the following order:\\n   - Weather\\n   - Trail name\\n   - Distance\\n   - Estimated time\\n   - Elevation\\n   - Shade level\\n4. One short sentence explaining why this trail fits today.\\n5. One calm, positive closing sentence.\\n\\nUse the following data:\\nWeather: {{ $json.weatherSummary }}, {{ $json.temperature }}°C\\nTrail name: {{ $json.Name }}\\nDistance: {{ $json.Miles }} miles\\nEstimated time: {{ $json.Time }}\\nElevation: {{ $json.Elevation }}\\nShade level: {{ $json['Shade Level'] }}\\n\\nRules:\\n- Keep the email under 130 words\\n- Use simple, professional language\\n- Do NOT mention AI, automation, or models\\n- Do NOT use emojis\\n- Use short paragraphs\\n\\nOutput only the email body text.\",\n  \"stream\": false\n}\n",
